Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I got divorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's more like my wife ran away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd paid more attention to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She left me because I paid more attention to this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what she said to me:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're just a collector who peeks into people's hearts."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My talent for fishing around in the abyss of\Npeople's hearts also carries a high risk\Nof sinking into that abyss myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fourth victim was an 18-year-old girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the sexual arousal\Nyou felt when you chopped her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me about the twelfth murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanna Kempf of Krupp-Haus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty-two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When I did that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to tell\Nme about that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll want to ask\Nabout it sometime in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but for now, I'd like to ask\Nabout the first eleven incidents,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, is the peak of your sexual arousal\Nusually before or after you kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see there, his victims are limited to\Nmissing school girls from the ages of 16 to 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:01.36,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(360,340)}Monster's Abyss
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His crimes should obviously be\Nclassified as sexual murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He confessed to a twelfth murder, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim of this murder was a 52-year-old\Nwoman named Kempf, and on top of\Nthat, there was no evidence of sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He claims that he did this at the request of\Na friend,  and our investigation is in a\Nstate of confusion due to his claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this was the only way I could reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm a serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just heard rumors in the papers, on the\Nnews, and from old college colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you come here to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that we're good friends, especially since...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you've had nothing but contempt for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I feel when I look into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that you despised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to give back that money I borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you're one of\Nthe top criminal psychologists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I want you to take a look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me! Look at me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me has\Ngrown so big, Doctor Tenma!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Help me! The monster inside me is about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This Johan is the real killer of the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed the foster parents that took care of him, left\Nyou those messages, and once again disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find him as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, prove your\Ninnocence as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty years ago, there was a kid at a famous\Nmedical school who didn't rest until\Nhe became the top of his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When a Japanese student came to that school,\Nhis situation changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sociable and popular with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, his grades were excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The student who was at the top of the class\Nwas displaced during the midterm exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He worked his hardest for the finals so that\Nhe could become the top student again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He had done perfectly in\Nall of his classes until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but the last test was his worst subject:\NIntroduction to Medical Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If he did poorly on that test, all his hard\Nwork would have been for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That man played his last card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only way he could get the high score.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Japanese man didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The result was that the man took back\Nhis position as the top student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you have any ideas\Nabout those two messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your theory that of multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to say that one personality is a\Nmurderer, and the other personality\Nis trying to stop those murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are, of course, examples of serial killers\Nleaving messages like this behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's also the possibility that they're using\Nthis to escape from being guilty of their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing through that is where we\Npsychoanalysts show our skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people think that all serial killers are\Nintroverts, but they are sadly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them are intelligent,\Nsociable, and very persuasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all big fat liars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that he's just playing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. You shouldn't rush to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell me more about Johan, first?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I got divorced three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's more like my wife ran away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a fascinating conversation, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like to research this in further detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in touch with me in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster he was talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, they exist... inside of you,\Ninside of him, even inside of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your academic nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that monsters really exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me with those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate being looked down on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are much more frightening things in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's definitely going to see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When he does, I'll contact you at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After you arrest him, I'd like you\Nto let me use him for research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fascinating criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the Kempf Mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to the basement storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The proof that monsters exist is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Kohl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten in touch with Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,8:00 P.M. in Oder Park, in front of the fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently following the route of entry\Nthat Jurgens used to commit his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,According to his confession, he snuck in through\Nthis storage room and spent a few hours here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When she came home, he snuck up to the\Nsecond-floor bedroom and killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing unusual here... just pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They have Mrs. Kempf in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no proof that there's a monster\Nlike Jurgens said there was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Jurgens committed this murder\Nto throw the investigators off his trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He claimed that he killed at\Nthe request of his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He called that friend a "monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, my mother\Nwould always punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a large doll that\Nshe loved very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a female doll with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was beaten, I pleaded\Nwith the doll to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but it would only look at me and grin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There were just a lot of\Nphotos in that storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter where I looked, it was just\Nmy mother, my mother, my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,always watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that Jurgens changed this storage room\Nto look like the room from his childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Jurgens as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be. He couldn't have\Nknown Mrs. Kempf as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jurgens' face as a child was put on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, too. This... this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kempf was not supposed to have had any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this boy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The proof that monsters exist is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just did everything exactly as the\Nletters from my friend told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I got a letter in a\Nblank envelope with no address.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote to me in an overly familiar\Nway, and at first I was angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I got a letter every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a letter demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the letters didn't come as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gradually, I started enjoying receiving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Those letters were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that he might really be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day, he called me with that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Go look at the basement in that mansion..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The storage room in the basement\Nof Mrs. Kempf's mansion...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he know about my childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was totally confused, there\Nin the basement storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mrs. Kempf my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to my senses, I went up\Nto the second floor and killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a letter demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that "friend" send letters to Mrs. Kempf, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me! Look at me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me has grown so big!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Help! The monster inside me\Nis about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the messages that Johan left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The friend and Johan are real...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's past eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Kohl, look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an Asian man with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for bothering you\Nat such a busy time, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I analyzed what you'd said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Johan doesn't exist."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"He's just something you made up."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out, Rudy. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently researching a\Nserial killer named Jurgens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one incident where the modus\Noperandi is different from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today. Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The carnival is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell all the groups, "When I give the\Nsignal, move in and capture him."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to listen to their conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, you looked down on me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you saw me cheating, you've\Nalways looked down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Kohl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma and the doctor are\Nwalking towards the west exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get lost in the crowd leaving the carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve all the scorn you can give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudy, more importantly, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I used that hidden paper to cheat on the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Run! You're surrounded by the police!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look, just walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the doctor being threatened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowd is too loud. I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jurgens said that he killed\Nat the request of his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in Mrs. Kempf's storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kempf didn't have any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Johan you spoke of and Jurgens'\Nfriend are probably one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're outside the west gate.\NShould we stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Tenma might have a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kempf had letters that had the same\Nmessages as the letters he left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan was feeding off of her, and when\Nher use had run out, he disposed of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have been to eliminate his past, just as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can't tell you anything more than that,\Nbut from what I've analyzed, I can tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how, but\NJohan can sniff out the killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he can\Nisolate them and control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find the case where Johan had killed\Nhis foster parents after adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because he thought that foster\Nparents weren't necessary anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can think of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan found his ideal family and joined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he trying to erase his past, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have some reason for doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he joining his family for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, for what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we've made it to the bus terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready. Find out which bus he gets on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround the terminal with the squad cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got you a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still ways to\Nprove that you're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not chasing after Johan to clear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to... to Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I never looked down on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked like an interesting fellow,\Nbut I never had a chance to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we're finally friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me cheat, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You lifted your head and looked my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cheating, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.73,0:22:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Five buses left at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:53.55,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}Journey to Freiham
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:36.79,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And slowly, you come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:44.38,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all as it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.81,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can only do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:59.40,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you're game enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:07.20,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You could place your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.29,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the love of life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.63,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.39,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.31,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But we'll go down fighting

